<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shén yī dìng néng 迦南989</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 xiǎng dào wǒ men de hái zi, wǒ men dōu yǒu dān xīn. lái ba wǒ men xiàn zài bǎ tā men jiāo gěi shén.
 wǒ men bù néng wú suǒ bù zài, dàn wǒ men yǐ jīng zhī dào, shén bì yǔ tā men tóng zài.
 wǒ men bù néng wú suǒ bù zhī, dàn wǒ men dōu zhī dào, shén yī dìng néng.
 wǒ men dōu bù néng zuò dé wán měi, dàn wǒ men dōu zhī dào, shén yī dìng néng.
 wǒ men zhēn chéng de lái yǎng wàng zhǔ, bǎ wǒ men suǒ yǒu de nán chù dōu jiāo gěi zhǔ.
 tā bì juàn gù, tā bì bǎo hù, tā bì cì fú. yīn wèi tā shì wǒ men xìn kào de zhǔ.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>989</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>